-- Progressive to take controlling stake in ARX Holding for $875 mln
-- By Rohit T. K. in Bengaluru
-- Tue Dec 16, 2014 09:07AM EST
-- None



Dec 16 (Reuters) - Progressive Corp <PGR.N>, a provider of auto insurance products, said it would acquire a controlling stake in property insurer ARX Holding Corp for $875 million in cash.

Progressive Corp said it would increase its share in the parent of American Strategic Insurance to 67 percent from 5 percent after it buys shares from non-management shareholders. [ID:nHUG37gyYF] American Strategic Insurance, which provides personal and commercial property insurance, will continue as a separate company.